history.content: It would be the same way you enroll in the school year. If you go to the academics tab in cal central right underneath the class enrollment tab, you can choose which term you want to add classes for, and you would do the whole thing of creating a schedule in the schedule planner and importing the cart or add the class numbers directly in the class enrollment tab.  Oh and also make sure you're in the right term in the class enrollment page, there should be a change term button near the top if you aren't.
